==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: fūqī bĕn shì tóng lín niăo
===Proverb===
'''[[夫妻]][[本]][[是]][[同]][[林]][[鳥]]'''
# Even though a husband and wife were originally birds from the same forest (...when adversity strikes, they fly in separate directions).

===Alternate forms===
